title: Donkey of the Day - I Can't Believe It's Not Milk
itunes:title: Donkey of the Day - I Can't Believe It's Not Milk
description:
Today on the show Charlamagne gave "Donkey of the Day" to dministrators of the RALLY summer school program in Juneau for giving students floor sealant instead of milk to drink at breakfast.

See omnystudio.com/listener for privacy information.
